===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*-tus}}
From {{inh|en|enm|yest}}, {{m|enm|yeest}}, {{m|enm|gest}}, {{m|enm|gist}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ġist}}, {{m|ang|ġyst}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*jestu}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*jestuz}}. Cognate with {{cog|stq|Jääst|t=yeast}}, {{cog|fy|gêst}}, {{m|fy|gist|t=yeast}}, {{cog|nl|gist|t=yeast}}, {{cog|nds-de|Gest|t=yeast}}, {{cog|de|Gischt|t=sea foam}}, {{cog|sv|jäst|t=yeast}}, {{cog|no|jest|t=yeast}}, {{cog|is|jöstur|t=yeast}}.
